title: Did Minneapolis Police Arrest U.S. Rep. Ilhan Omar on Suspicion of Trespassing in 2013?
subtitle: Some of Omar's opponents and critics have highlighted a six-year-old incident at the Hotel Ivy in downtown Minneapolis.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In January 2013, future U.S. Rep. Ilhan Omar was arrested on suspicion of trespass in Minneapolis.
